            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">I(ovi) O(ptimo) M(aximo)</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Ux</supplied>l<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">emitano</supplied> pro <lb n="3"/>salute <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan></supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> tem<supplied reason="lost">plum vetus</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>tate con<supplied reason="lost">lapsum</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="6"/>Magnus <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan>? <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="7"/>procurat<supplied reason="lost">oris <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> restituit</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Dolenz - de Bernardo Stempel: abweichende Interpretation und Ergänzung: [---]l[---] / [--- pro] / salute [Imp(eratoris) ---] / Aug(usti) tem[plum vetus]/tate con[lapsum ---] / Magnus [adsess(or)] procur(atoris) [f(errariarum) N(oricarum) rest(ituit)].</p>
            </div>
